        <abstract> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi> [2d ed.] will soon be published.</p>  
<p>1000 more copies of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> [2d ed.] will soon have to be printed, so CD could send any alterations to be made in the plates.</p> 
